Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團..長？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓它吞下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被吞進肚子裡之前 應該還能救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度的絕望 別以為能夠阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄不適合我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不適合你我..不適合所有人！
